<li id="cite_note-RTBCh2-7">^ <a href="#cite_ref-RTBCh2_7-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-RTBCh2_7-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-RTBCh2_7-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <i><a href="/wiki/Releasing_the_Bonds" title="Releasing the Bonds">Releasing the Bonds</a>: Empowering People to Think for Themselves</i>, Steven Hassan, Ch. 2, Aitan Publishing Company, 2000</li>
